      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_4824723965347124956.png",
                "id": "talent96938",
                "key": "源流",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "源流"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷罰惡曜之眼</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/c29fd0841f95e044bae32d03dc31765a_7553403132942732674.png",
                "id": "talent38203",
                "key": "神變·惡曜開眼",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "神變·惡曜開眼"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>，其他我方角色獲得2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">充能</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/8d02cb476ba0314a99ce5e7ecc3b4904_5546833228455706521.png",
                "id": "talent44003",
                "key": "奧義·夢想真說",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "奧義·夢想真說"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】戰鬥開始時，初始附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">諸願百眼之輪</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">諸願百眼之輪</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方其他角色使用「元素爆發」後：</span>累積1點「願力」。（最多累積3點）</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色使用奧義·夢想真說時：</span>消耗所有「願力」，每點「願力」使造成的傷害+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/f18816cd4d10b81b8610917baa51d71a_8401914935961442363.png",
                "id": "talent70341",
                "key": "諸願百眼之輪",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "諸願百眼之輪"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：3</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">此召喚物在場時：</span>我方角色「元素爆發」造成的傷害+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/7998136/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3853556567559295333.png",
                "key": "雷罰惡曜之眼",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/7998136/75f1d2ef52221da67ee1c52ce97af966_3400528827984324418.png",
                "title": "雷罰惡曜之眼"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著雷元素，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素傷害+1的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[激化領域]</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/7998136/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_7979506267479743016.png",
                "key": "雷元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">充能</span></strong></p><p>角色使用「元素爆發」時，需要消耗充能。</p><p>角色使用「元素戰技」或「普通攻擊」後，會獲得1點充能。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/7998136/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_5392278406733579903.png",
                "key": "規則解釋",
